Suggested Usage
	Keep the HTML file and encrypted files on a USB drive / memory stick
	Use strong, memorable passphrases
	Back up important encrypted files


🌐 Philosophy
This tool reflects a simple idea: Your privacy is YOURS. Encryption 1 — Online Version focuses on practical, accessible security.

